        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4507",
        "content": "Slang is odious!",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4507_16021_000018_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4507/16021/4507_16021_000018_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4507",
        "content": "Slang makes one shudder!\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4507_16021_000019_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4507/16021/4507_16021_000019_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4507",
        "content": "Who denies that?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4507_16021_000019_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4507/16021/4507_16021_000019_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4507",
        "content": "Of course it does.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4507_16021_000020_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4507/16021/4507_16021_000020_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4507",
        "content": "When it is a question of probing a wound, a gulf, a society, since when has it been considered wrong to go too far? to go to the bottom?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4507_16021_000020_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4507/16021/4507_16021_000020_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4507",
        "content": "Why should one halt on the way?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4507_16021_000021_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4507/16021/4507_16021_000021_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4507",
        "content": "Nothing is more lugubrious than the contemplation thus in its nudity, in the broad light of thought, of the horrible swarming of slang.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4507_16021_000021_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4507/16021/4507_16021_000021_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4507",
        "content": "It seems, in fact, to be a sort of horrible beast made for the night which has just been torn from its cesspool.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4507_16021_000021_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4507/16021/4507_16021_000021_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4507",
        "content": "One thinks one beholds a frightful, living, and bristling thicket which quivers, rustles, wavers, returns to shadow, threatens and glares.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4507_16021_000021_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4507/16021/4507_16021_000021_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4507",
        "content": "One word resembles a claw, another an extinguished and bleeding eye, such and such a phrase seems to move like the claw of a crab.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4507_16021_000022_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4507/16021/4507_16021_000022_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4507",
        "content": "Now, when has horror ever excluded study?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4507_16021_000022_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4507/16021/4507_16021_000022_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4507",
        "content": "Since when has malady banished medicine?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4507_16021_000022_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4507/16021/4507_16021_000022_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4507",
        "content": "He would be like a philologist refusing to examine a fact in language, a philosopher hesitating to scrutinize a fact in humanity.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4507_16021_000022_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4507/16021/4507_16021_000022_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4507",
        "content": "For, it must be stated to those who are ignorant of the case, that argot is both a literary phenomenon and a social result.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4507_16021_000022_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4507/16021/4507_16021_000022_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4507",
        "content": "What is slang, properly speaking?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4507_16021_000022_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4507/16021/4507_16021_000022_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4507",
        "content": "It is the language of wretchedness.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4507_16021_000023_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4507/16021/4507_16021_000023_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4507",
        "content": "We may be stopped; the fact may be put to us in general terms, which is one way of attenuating it; we may be told, that all trades, professions, it may be added, all the accidents of the social hierarchy and all forms of intelligence, have their own slang.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4507_16021_000023_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4507/16021/4507_16021_000023_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4507",
        "content": "The painter who says: \"My grinder,\" the notary who says: \"My Skip the Gutter,\" the hairdresser who says: \"My mealyback,\" the cobbler who says: \"My cub,\" talks slang. Strictly speaking, if one absolutely insists on the point, all the different fashions of saying the right and the left, the sailor's port and starboard, the scene shifter's court side, and garden side, the beadle's Gospel side and Epistle side, are slang.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4507_16021_000023_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4507/16021/4507_16021_000023_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4507",
        "content": "The sugar manufacturer who says: \"Loaf, clarified, lumps, bastard, common, burnt,\"--this honest manufacturer talks slang.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4507_16021_000023_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4507/16021/4507_16021_000023_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4507",
        "content": "A certain school of criticism twenty years ago, which used to say: \"Half of the works of Shakespeare consists of plays upon words and puns,\"--talked slang.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4507_16021_000023_000010",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4507/16021/4507_16021_000023_000010.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4507",
        "content": "The classic Academician who calls flowers \"Flora,\" fruits, \"Pomona,\" the sea, \"Neptune,\" love, \"fires,\" beauty, \"charms,\" a horse, \"a courser,\" the white or tricolored cockade, \"the rose of Bellona,\" the three cornered hat, \"Mars' triangle,\"--that classical Academician talks slang.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4507_16021_000024_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4507/16021/4507_16021_000024_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4507",
        "content": "No doubt.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4507_16021_000024_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4507/16021/4507_16021_000024_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4507",
        "content": "For our part, we reserve to the word its ancient and precise, circumscribed and determined significance, and we restrict slang to slang.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4507_16021_000024_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4507/16021/4507_16021_000024_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4507",
        "content": "To meet the needs of this conflict, wretchedness has invented a language of combat, which is slang.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4507_16021_000025_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4507/16021/4507_16021_000025_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4507",
        "content": "To keep afloat and to rescue from oblivion, to hold above the gulf, were it but a fragment of some language which man has spoken and which would, otherwise, be lost, that is to say, one of the elements, good or bad, of which civilization is composed, or by which it is complicated, to extend the records of social observation; is to serve civilization itself.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4507_16021_000025_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4507/16021/4507_16021_000025_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4507",
        "content": "This service Plautus rendered, consciously or unconsciously, by making two Carthaginian soldiers talk Phoenician; that service Moliere rendered, by making so many of his characters talk Levantine and all sorts of dialects.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4507_16021_000025_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4507/16021/4507_16021_000025_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4507",
        "content": "Phoenician, very good! Levantine, quite right!",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4507_16021_000025_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4507/16021/4507_16021_000025_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4507",
        "content": "Even dialect, let that pass!",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4507_16021_000025_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4507/16021/4507_16021_000025_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4507",
        "content": "They are tongues which have belonged to nations or provinces; but slang!",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4507_16021_000025_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4507/16021/4507_16021_000025_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4507",
        "content": "What is the use of preserving slang?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4507_16021_000026_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4507/16021/4507_16021_000026_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4507",
        "content": "To this we reply in one word, only.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4507_16021_000026_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4507/16021/4507_16021_000026_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4507",
        "content": "Assuredly, if the tongue which a nation or a province has spoken is worthy of interest, the language which has been spoken by a misery is still more worthy of attention and study.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4507_16021_000027_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4507/16021/4507_16021_000027_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4507",
        "content": "It is the language which has been spoken, in France, for example, for more than four centuries, not only by a misery, but by every possible human misery.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4507_16021_000028_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4507/16021/4507_16021_000028_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4507",
        "content": "Have these historians of hearts and souls duties at all inferior to the historians of external facts?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4507_16021_000028_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4507/16021/4507_16021_000028_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4507",
        "content": "Does any one think that Alighieri has any fewer things to say than Machiavelli?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4507_16021_000028_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4507/16021/4507_16021_000028_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4507",
        "content": "Is the under side of civilization any less important than the upper side merely because it is deeper and more sombre?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4507_16021_000029_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4507/16021/4507_16021_000029_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4507",
        "content": "Let us say, moreover, parenthetically, that from a few words of what precedes a marked separation might be inferred between the two classes of historians which does not exist in our mind.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4507_16021_000029_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4507/16021/4507_16021_000029_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4507",
        "content": "The history of manners and ideas permeates the history of events, and this is true reciprocally.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4507_16021_000029_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4507/16021/4507_16021_000029_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4507",
        "content": "They constitute two different orders of facts which correspond to each other, which are always interlaced, and which often bring forth results.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4507_16021_000029_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4507/16021/4507_16021_000029_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4507",
        "content": "All the lineaments which providence traces on the surface of a nation have their parallels, sombre but distinct, in their depths, and all convulsions of the depths produce ebullitions on the surface.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4507_16021_000029_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4507/16021/4507_16021_000029_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4507",
        "content": "True history being a mixture of all things, the true historian mingles in everything.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4507_16021_000030_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4507/16021/4507_16021_000030_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4507",
        "content": "Man is not a circle with a single centre; he is an ellipse with a double focus.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4507_16021_000030_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4507/16021/4507_16021_000030_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4507",
        "content": "Facts form one of these, and ideas the other.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4507_16021_000031_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4507/16021/4507_16021_000031_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4507",
        "content": "There it clothes itself in word masks, in metaphor rags.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4507_16021_000031_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4507/16021/4507_16021_000031_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4507",
        "content": "In this guise it becomes horrible.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4507_16021_000032_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4507/16021/4507_16021_000032_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4507",
        "content": "One finds it difficult to recognize.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4507_16021_000032_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4507/16021/4507_16021_000032_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4507",
        "content": "Is it really the French tongue, the great human tongue?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4507_16021_000032_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4507/16021/4507_16021_000032_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4507",
        "content": "Behold it ready to step upon the stage and to retort upon crime, and prepared for all the employments of the repertory of evil.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4507_16021_000033_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4507/16021/4507_16021_000033_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4507",
        "content": "When one listens, by the side of honest men, at the portals of society, one overhears the dialogues of those who are on the outside. One distinguishes questions and replies.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4507_16021_000033_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4507/16021/4507_16021_000033_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4507",
        "content": "One perceives, without understanding it, a hideous murmur, sounding almost like human accents, but more nearly resembling a howl than an articulate word.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4507_16021_000033_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4507/16021/4507_16021_000033_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4507",
        "content": "It is slang. The words are misshapen and stamped with an indescribable and fantastic bestiality.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4507_16021_000033_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4507/16021/4507_16021_000033_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4507",
        "content": "One thinks one hears hydras talking.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4507_16021_000034_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4507/16021/4507_16021_000034_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4507",
        "content": "It is unintelligible in the dark.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4507_16021_000034_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4507/16021/4507_16021_000034_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4507",
        "content": "It gnashes and whispers, completing the gloom with mystery.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4507_16021_000034_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4507/16021/4507_16021_000034_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4507",
        "content": "It is black in misfortune, it is blacker still in crime; these two blacknesses amalgamated, compose slang.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4507_16021_000034_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4507/16021/4507_16021_000034_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4507",
        "content": "Obscurity in the atmosphere, obscurity in acts, obscurity in voices.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4507_16021_000035_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4507/16021/4507_16021_000035_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4507",
        "content": "Let us have compassion on the chastised.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4507_16021_000035_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4507/16021/4507_16021_000035_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4507",
        "content": "Alas!",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4507_16021_000035_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4507/16021/4507_16021_000035_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4507",
        "content": "Who are we ourselves?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4507_16021_000035_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4507/16021/4507_16021_000035_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4507",
        "content": "The earth is not devoid of resemblance to a jail.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4507_16021_000035_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4507/16021/4507_16021_000035_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4507",
        "content": "Who knows whether man is not a recaptured offender against divine justice?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4507_16021_000035_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4507/16021/4507_16021_000035_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4507",
        "content": "Look closely at life.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4507_16021_000035_000009",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4507/16021/4507_16021_000035_000009.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4507",
        "content": "It is so made, that everywhere we feel the sense of punishment.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4507_16021_000036_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4507/16021/4507_16021_000036_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4507",
        "content": "Are you what is called a happy man?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4507_16021_000036_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4507/16021/4507_16021_000036_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4507",
        "content": "Well! you are sad every day.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4507_16021_000036_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4507/16021/4507_16021_000036_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4507",
        "content": "Each day has its own great grief or its little care.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4507_16021_000036_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4507/16021/4507_16021_000036_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4507",
        "content": "This without reckoning in the pains of the heart.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4507_16021_000036_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4507/16021/4507_16021_000036_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4507",
        "content": "And so it goes on.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4507_16021_000036_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4507/16021/4507_16021_000036_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4507",
        "content": "One cloud is dispelled, another forms.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4507_16021_000036_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4507/16021/4507_16021_000036_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4507",
        "content": "There is hardly one day out of a hundred which is wholly joyous and sunny.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4507_16021_000036_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4507/16021/4507_16021_000036_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4507",
        "content": "And you belong to that small class who are happy!",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4507_16021_000036_000009",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4507/16021/4507_16021_000036_000009.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4507",
        "content": "As for the rest of mankind, stagnating night rests upon them.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4507_16021_000037_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4507/16021/4507_16021_000037_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4507",
        "content": "Thoughtful minds make but little use of the phrase: the fortunate and the unfortunate.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4507_16021_000037_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4507/16021/4507_16021_000037_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4507",
        "content": "In this world, evidently the vestibule of another, there are no fortunate.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4507_16021_000038_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4507/16021/4507_16021_000038_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4507",
        "content": "To diminish the number of the shady, to augment the number of the luminous,--that is the object.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4507_16021_000038_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4507/16021/4507_16021_000038_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4507",
        "content": "That is why we cry: Education! science!",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4507_16021_000038_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4507/16021/4507_16021_000038_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4507",
        "content": "To teach reading, means to light the fire; every syllable spelled out sparkles.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4507_16021_000039_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4507/16021/4507_16021_000039_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4507",
        "content": "However, he who says light does not, necessarily, say joy.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4507_16021_000039_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4507/16021/4507_16021_000039_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4507",
        "content": "People suffer in the light; excess burns.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4507_16021_000039_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4507/16021/4507_16021_000039_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4507",
        "content": "The flame is the enemy of the wing.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4507_16021_000039_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4507/16021/4507_16021_000039_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4507",
        "content": "To burn without ceasing to fly,--therein lies the marvel of genius.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4507_16021_000040_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4507/16021/4507_16021_000040_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4507",
        "content": "When you shall have learned to know, and to love, you will still suffer. The day is born in tears.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    }
]